<div id="action-power_off" class="">
    <div data-bind="visible: selectedBucket().status() == 'active'">
        <p>This will power off your droplet.</p>
        <p>We recommend powering off your droplet through the command line, as this action is the same as hard resetting the server and may cause data corruption.</p>
        <p>Do you wish to proceed?</p>
        <div><input type="submit" value="Power Off" data-bind="click: selectedBucket().powerOffBucket"></div>
    </div>
    <div data-bind="visible: selectedBucket().status() != 'active'">
        <p>This will boot your droplet</p>
        <input type="submit" value="Boot" data-bind="click: selectedBucket().bootBucket">
    </div>
</div>
<div class="" id="action-power_cycle">
<p>This will reboot your droplet.</p>
<p>We recommend rebooting your droplet through the command line, as this action is the same as hard resetting the server and may cause data corruption.</p>
<p>Do you wish to proceed?</p>
<form action="/droplets/341045/power_cycle" class="button_to" data-remote="true" method="post"><div><input type="submit" value="Power Cycle"></div></form>
</div>

<div id="action-console" class="">
<p>This will open up a console VNC connection to your droplet and is the equivalent of plugging a monitor and keyboard directly to your virtual server.</p>
Console Access (coming soon)
</div>
<div id="action-reset_root_password">
<p>This will shut down your droplet and a new root password will be set and emailed to you.</p>
<p>Do you wish to proceed?</p>
Reset Root Password (coming soon)
</div>

<p data-bind="visible: selectedBucket().status() != 'active'">After the resize is finished Boot it from the control panel: "Power" > "Boot".</p>

<p><strong>Please note: We will begin charging for automated backups starting on July 1st, 2013.</strong> You will receive your first bill for enabled backups on August 1st, 2013.
